{"tid":25422,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"邊張信用卡最好用？","createTime":"2016-12-06T06:12:56.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T00:52:19.000Z","uid":4705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ac19e6f6953e63644917bf867aa5e2690ac01afc","tid":25422,"uid":4705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:12:56.000Z","msg":"大學生 唔算成日碌卡<br />\n用緊大學個張學生卡<br />\n但略嫌少優惠/冇乜著數<br />\n有冇邊張最抵玩/最著數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bdb2a9235e20a017bf37e31ffcfcb2753e0653a","tid":25422,"uid":4705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c8accb284edd955a9ae67796cf6e5b8b48d155","tid":25422,"uid":19933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:24:12.000Z","msg":"One+<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18c189d822fce6432c5d59ddd9d19ed3e74e9092","tid":25422,"uid":6245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:25:49.000Z","msg":"匯豐"},{"pid":"8e04ed85c812a5b65eb0650f1845599a8e50c10b","tid":25422,"uid":16201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:28:22.000Z","msg":"碌得少既話優惠多與少有咩影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學生既話應該都係得enjoy卡比較好<br />\n200$換1$ cash dollars<br />\n用黎交埋42100$學費有3倍分（有上限宜家）<br />\n怡和旗下就100$換1$<br />\n1年都應該收到400$既大約"},{"pid":"6ddb45057529193afd888d9f2fbd9f7d7e927ad3","tid":25422,"uid":39122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:35:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大學生 唔算成日碌卡<br />\n<br />\n用緊大學個張學生卡<br />\n<br />\n但略嫌少優惠/冇乜著數<br />\n<br />\n有冇邊張最抵玩/最著數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一般信用卡講緊公價 0.4% 回贈，高過呢個比率你就己經叫有著數。<br />\n但係呢類通常又有好多條款，例如上面講嗰張 one+ 雖然話有 1% 回贈，不過交學費、自動轉賬嗰啲係一蚊回贈都冇。總之銀行唔會死錯人。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\none+ 係其中一張八達通自動增值去到 1% 回贈嘅卡，你可以照玩住先，到你發現你好大洗之餘又有好特定嘅開支類別（例如成日課金或者幫屋企落超市買嘢），就可以玩卡海。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2c7118d03b6d4d90990a48d870825a4973222f","tid":25422,"uid":41803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:40:53.000Z","msg":"最抵玩一定不斷申請卡要迎新禮物然後一年後取消，再過多年又玩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119a078d46f5f00a32b4adcad0e31e760dc958c1","tid":25422,"uid":52611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:44:27.000Z","msg":"小弟用緊渣打萬事達白金行政人員，有1%回贈"},{"pid":"6afa25bcc7a7fc837106895e6e4b7170d4acd347","tid":25422,"uid":39122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:49:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟用緊渣打萬事達白金行政人員，有1%回贈</blockquote>我都用緊，佢比 one+ 好嘅地方係自動轉帳都有 1%，不過繳費仍然係冇。<br />\n而且最大問題係冇佢出糧戶口係申請唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe2b6dc9ea0bb289f8c211cb267fe406b7b4aa9","tid":25422,"uid":3328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:49:37.000Z","msg":"東亞都有1% 回贈"},{"pid":"f065e8e55ac89d4a5a99486788762f236bde4c9b","tid":25422,"uid":33039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:49:58.000Z","msg":"月入萬零蚊 想開張Hsbc 信用卡。邊張好"},{"pid":"88a0c9dbf13e2970410d9a1477d27b271255be08","tid":25422,"uid":39122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:54:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>月入萬零蚊 想開張Hsbc 信用卡。邊張好</blockquote>好似冇乜分別，主要都係靠「最紅自主獎賞」嚟食糊。"},{"pid":"68df561c27cb5c9dee0404464f9d6924924bf337","tid":25422,"uid":3047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:07:34.000Z","msg":"其實wewa卡好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f60f752450736f103527cc963bf352aa155849","tid":25422,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:13:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實wewa卡好唔好<i